    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow disposable e-cigarettes to be over 600puffs and 2ml tanks",
        "additional_details": "As there are over 1.3 million disposable e cigarettes binned every week and Therefore around 10 tonnes of Lithium is being chucked.\r\n\r\nEach disposable apparently only contains less than 1/10 of a gramme of Lithium but the sheer quantity being wasted adds up.\r\nSo if you allow disposable e-cigarettes to be over 600 puffs with rechargeable batteries there will be less waste of lithium and plastic.",
        "background": "To legalise disposable e-cigarettes over 600 puffs and 2ml tanks.",
